==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interpellate
<hw>In`ter*pel"late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Interpel</er>.]</ety> <def>To question imperatively, as a minister,
or other executive officer, in explanation of his conduct; -- generally
on the part of a legislative body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interpellation</ent>⟦br⟧
